snippet.title: Best VGM 838 - Zelda : Spirit Tracks - In the Fields
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2105 - https://youtu.be/nvv6JrhcQSo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Zelda : Spirit Tracks (2009)
In the Fields
Koji Kondo, Toru Minegishi, Asuka Ota & Manaka Tominaga
